                            <comment id="15905410" author="gopalv" created="Fri, 10 Mar 2017 17:06:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think there&apos;s enough contention on this lock from many threads - last I counted it was just 2 threads, so the performance should remain relatively identical.&lt;/p&gt;

